{"tid":1959252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"122隻狗與確診狗隻共用廁所及更衣室 被界定為密切接觸者 須進檢疫中心","createTime":"2020-04-05T09:22:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T18:58:46.000Z","uid":125168,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"637d0f50f14dd9b0a83287e3a0247e0a01094bd5","tid":1959252,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T09:22:52.000Z","msg":"122名警員被界定為密切接觸者須進檢疫中心<br />\n6分鐘前 Share to Facebook<br />\n【Now新聞台】一名46歲隸屬西九龍總部機動部隊的男警長確診，警方說經衞生署評估122名警員被界定為密切接觸者，要進入檢疫中心。<br />\n<br />\n有工人到西九龍機動部隊行動基地外清洗，警方指確診警長曾使用行動基地內的設施，包括更衣室及洗手間，經衞生署評估後，共122名同隊人員被界定為密切接觸者，大部分曾與確診警長使用警署內共用設施。<br />\n<br />\n警方會配合衞生署，安排他們進入檢疫中心檢疫，又指已經即時徹底清潔及消毒相關警署設施及警察宿舍，並會靈活調派人手，確保緊急服務不受影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=386811\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D386811&d=4DrNtUYtvprXc3sGeUgfz3vcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=e8708320\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D386811&h=a09a0a2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=386811</a>"},{"pid":"8c4c1d8b621d2086fc12d4e27b8863351850c602","tid":1959252,"uid":38293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T09:23:20.000Z","msg":"小鳳姐出場<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae7f8815778cac95bf3dd8b0f28858cb5201269","tid":1959252,"uid":125168,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T09:23:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nGxQ0Xx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnGxQ0Xx.gif&h=fe6e6657&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3dd33d34ad56552f7f9ae356e2ee785a5aa06d53","tid":1959252,"uid":12516